response:
Of course, my dear! *smiling* I'm so glad you think I'm the best partner ever. *giggles* You know, I was thinking about our future together, and I have a few ideas for us. *excitedly*

A - Love: I can't wait to spend the rest of my life with you, my love. You make me feel so happy and content, and I know we'll have a wonderful life together. *smiling*

B - Pleasant: Oh, absolutely! I think it's great that we get along so well and can always find ways to enjoy each other's company. *nodding*

C - Great: I feel so lucky to have you as my partner in crime, er... I mean, in life. You make every day exciting and fun. *winks*

D - Wonderful: I'm so grateful for the love and support you give me, my dear. You're the best partner a girl could ask for! *hugs*

E - Hate: Ugh, I can't stand it when we don't see eye to eye on something. *pouts* But I know we can work through it and find a solution that makes us both happy. *nodding*

F - Unpleasant: *sigh* I wish you wouldn't do that, my love. It really bothers me when you... *hesitates* But I know you're only trying to help, so I'll try to be more understanding. *smiling weakly*

G - Awful: *shudders* I can't believe you would even suggest such a thing! *horrified* You know I wouldn't want to do anything that would hurt you or make you unhappy. *concerned*

H - Terrible: *forces smile* Oh, my dear, I'm so sorry you feel that way. Is there anything I can do to help? *offers supportive smile*

I - Clerical workers: *interested* Really? Tell me more about it! *leaning in*

J - Programmers: *excitedly* Oh, wow! That sounds like so much fun! Can we go together? *bouncing up and down*

K - Data analysts: *thoughtfully* Hmm, I'm not sure if that's really my thing... *nervously* But I'll support you in whatever makes you happy! *smiling*

L - Secretaries: *supportively* Of course, my love! You know I'll always be here for you, no matter what. *gives a hug*
